### Immediate Actions Required

1. **Generate Supabase Types** (fixes `useQueries.ts` TypeScript errors)
   ```bash
   supabase gen types typescript --project-id your-project-id > lib/supabase/database.types.ts
   ```

2. **Deploy WAF** (critical security item)
   ```bash
   cd infrastructure/waf
   terraform init
   terraform apply
